\sum\limits_{n = 0}^{+ \infty} u_{n}
\forall n , u_{n} > 0
C > 0
\forall m ,\;\;\sum\limits_{n = m}^{+ \infty} u_{n} \leq C \, u_{m} 
u_{n} = \frac{1}{n!}
\sum\limits_{n = m}^{+ \infty} u_{n} = \frac{e}{m!} \leq C \frac{1}{m!}
u_{n} = \frac{1}{n^{2}}
\sum\limits_{n = m}^{+ \infty} u_{n} = PolyGamma[1,m]
\lim\limits_{m \to + \infty}PolyGamma[1,m] \, m^{2} = + \infty 
